line_1: "Then laugh, and sport, and shun all dreryhed,
line_2: "Where bitter dole ne'er shows her hateful head,

line_1: "Then laugh, and sport, and shun all dreryhed,
line_2: "Both youth and eld the paths of pleasure tread;

line_1: "Then laugh, and sport, and shun all dreryhed,
line_2: "Catch flying bliss, ne be by ought foresaid;
